        `[TYPE]` --> ðŸš¦ Type of file (e.g., `b` for block device, `c` for character device, `p` for named pipe).
        `[MAJOR]` --> ðŸ”¢ Major number of the device (obtained from the system).
        `[MINOR]` --> ðŸ”¢ Minor number of the device (obtained from the system).

